---
// You can import any required scripts or components here
---

<section class="px-4 md:px-8 py-10 lg:py-14">
  <article class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:gap-24">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <small
        class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 w-fit py-1 px-2 rounded-full text-xs"
      >
        For Job Seeker's
      </small>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <h1 class="font-slab text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium">
            Your next role deserves <br class="hidden md:block" /> more than a job
            board.
          </h1>
          <p class="max-w-[640px] pt-4 text-sm md:text-base">
            You deserve a recruiter who actually calls you back.
          </p>
        </div>
        <button
          class="bg-[#1c15e0] text-white text-base lg:text-lg w-fit px-6 py-3 rounded-full shrink-0"
        >
          Show Me What's Out There
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-8 justify-between">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-4 px-6 py-8 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-lg border border-gray-200 flex-1"
      >
        <h1
          class="font-slab font-medium text-3xl lg:text-[36px] leading-tight lg:leading-10"
        >
          Someone who gets <br /> what you do.
        </h1>
        <img
          src="/jobseekercard-1.png"
          alt="Someone who gets what you do"
          class="mix-blend-luminosity object-contain"
        />
        <p class="max-w-full lg:max-w-[392px] text-sm md:text-base">
          Your recruiter comes from your industry. They know what your
          experience is worth and how to tell that story to the right employers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-4 px-6 py-8 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-lg border border-gray-200 flex-1"
      >
        <h1
          class="font-slab font-medium text-3xl lg:text-[36px] leading-tight lg:leading-10"
        >
          Roles you won't find <br /> anywhere else.
        </h1>
        <img
          src="/jobseekercard-2.png"
          alt="Roles you won't find anywhere else"
          class="mix-blend-luminosity object-contain"
        />
        <p class="max-w-full lg:max-w-[392px] text-sm md:text-base">
          A lot of what we work on never gets advertised. You get access before
          the job goes public.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-4 px-6 py-8 bg-[#f8f8f8] rounded-lg border border-gray-200 flex-1"
      >
        <h1
          class="font-slab font-medium text-3xl lg:text-[36px] leading-tight lg:leading-10"
        >
          No ghost jobs. <br /> No wasted interviews.
        </h1>
        <img
          src="/jobseekercard-3.png"
          alt="No ghost jobs. No wasted interviews."
          class="mix-blend-luminosity object-contain"
        />
        <p class="max-w-full lg:max-w-[392px] text-sm md:text-base">
          We won't put you forward for something that isn't right. Every role we
          bring you is one we'd take seriously ourselves.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
